this will make the island of ireland the centre of excellence in the future for food production .
mr president , commissioner , i too congratulate the rapporteur on his excellent work .
i am particularly pleased about the unanimity shown on this issue within the group .
it is therefore specified that , through the adoption of a regulation , the commission will replace the existing authorisations with authorisations linked to the person responsible for putting the additives into circulation .
